<div class="modal fade" id="arthub-modal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">

      <div class="modal-header">
        <h4 class="modal-title show-modal" id="exampleModalLabel">ArtHub</h4>
        <button type="button" class="close close-button close-btn" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
          <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="modal-body">

          <div class="show-container">
            <div class="image-holder">
              <%= image_tag("Arthub.jpg") %>
              <%= image_tag("PamperMe.jpg") %>
            </div>
            <div class="information">
              <p class="very-small-text-bold">What we did</p>
              <p class="very-small-text">Designed and developed an art renting website geared at art lovers that do not yet have the economy to finance the purchase of expensive art. These suits people looking to try beore buying something as expensive as a painting, people that like to change decoration often and people that can not afford an expensive painting full time.</p>
              <p class="very-small-text-bold">How we did it</p>
              <ul id="how">
                <li class="very-small-text">Refined the product idea with a clear need, target customer and product pitch.</li>
                <li class="very-small-text">Created the user journey, user stories and the required features.</li>
                <li class="very-small-text">Prepared a Figma design of the website to agree on colours, imaginery etc </li>
                <li class="very-small-text">Developed the website following design sprints and agile methodology</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="very-small-text-bold">Visit the website at:</p>
              <p class="very-small-text">https://arthub-aja.herokuapp.com/</p>
            </div>
          </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

